orts in Southeast Sulawesi]]\n\n\n{{Indonesia-airport-stub}}\n{{CSulawesi-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2014}}\n{{Infobox airport\n| name                   = Sugimanuru Airport\n| nativename             = <small>Bandar Udara Sugimanuru</small>\n| image                  = \n| IATA                   = RAQ\n| ICAO                   = WAWR\n| pushpin_map            = Indonesia Sulawesi#Indonesia\n| pushpin_map_caption    = Location of the Airport in [[Sulawesi]] and [[Indonesia]]\n| pushpin_label          = RAQ\n| pushpin_label_position = right\n| type                   = Public\n| owner                  = \n| operator               = Government\n| city-served            = [[Raha, Indonesia|Raha]]\n| location               = [[Muna Regency]], [[Southeast Sulawesi]], [[Sulawesi]], [[Indonesia]]\n| metric-elev            = y\n| elevation-m            = 74.63\n| elevation-f            = 244.85\n| coordinates            = {{coord|04|45|38|S|122|34|09.7|E|region:ID_type:airport|display=it}}<ref>http://hubud.dephub.go.id/?id+info_bandara+detail+79</ref>\n| website                = \n| metric-rwy             = y\n| r1-number              = 08/26<ref>[[:id:Bandar Udara Sugimanuru]]</ref>\n| r1-length-m            = 1600\n| r1-length-f            = 5249\n| r1-surface             = Asphalt\n| footnotes              = \n}}\n\n'''Sugimanuru Airport''' ({{lang-id|Bandar Udara Sugimanuru}}) {{airport codes|RAQ|WAWR}}, is a domestic airport located at [[Raha, Indonesia|Raha]], the capital of [[Muna Regency]], [[Southeast Sulawesi]] province on the [[islands of Indonesia|island]] of [[Sulawesi]] in Indonesia.\n\n==Airlines and Destinations==\n{{airport-dest-list\n| [[Garuda Indonesia]] | [[Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport|Makassar]]\n| [[Wings Air]] | [[Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport|Makassar]]<ref>https://agent.lionair.co.id/LionAirAgentsPortal/Default.aspx</ref>\n}}\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n<!--Navigation box-->\n{{Airports in Indonesia}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Airports in Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Southeast Sulawesi]]\n[[Category:Transport in Southeast Sulawesi]]\n[[Category:Airports in Sulawesi]]\n\n\n{{Indonesia-airport-stub}}\n{{CSulawesi-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "OktaRama2010", "label": "safe", "comment": "- 3 categories; \u00b1Category:Airports in Sulawesi\u2192Category:Airports in Southeast SulawesiusingHotCat", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sugimanuru_Airport"}
